Source: pi-puck-boot
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Russell Joyce <russell.joyce@york.ac.uk>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>=9)
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Homepage: https://github.com/yorkrobotlab/pi-puck

Package: pi-puck-boot
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, wiringpi
Description: Pi-puck boot configuration
 Includes device tree overlay, config.txt additions and other configuration
 files for booting Raspbian on the Pi-puck. Also sets hostname on boot from
 '/boot/hostname' file (if it exists).
